dct_title_s: Plat book of Genesee County, Michigan
dct_description_sm: Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners.
Notes: Publication date estimated by absence of Michigan highway numbers, in comparison with later Hixson plat book of Genesee County that shows Michigan highway numbers.
